OL,6,FA teacher who was forced to 'pull
OL,7,Fgirls' off the bus has said the teens
OL,8,Fwere rescued just seconds before
OL,9,Fdisaster.
OL,11,FTzivia Yodaiken said: "We were pulling
OL,12,Fgirls off the bus. If it had been one
OL,13,Fsecond later we would've all died. The
OL,14,Fsecond the last girl got off the bus
OL,15,Fit exploded."
OL,17,FThe 19-year-old said the back of the
OL,18,Fvehicle was already on fire when the
OL,19,Fgroup of between 30 and 40 Year 9 and
OL,20,F10 girls from Jewish High School began
OL,21,Fto smell smoke at around 7pm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
