OL,6,FShortly after, the bus's fire alarm
OL,7,Fwent off, prompting an evacuation.
OL,9,FThe school had been on a trip to
OL,10,FBotany Bay in Chorley when the blaze
OL,11,Fbroke out.J"I turned around and the
OL,12,Fback of the bus was in flames," Tzivia
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FFirefighters worked to tackle the
OL,16,Fblaze. Police say all passengers and
OL,17,Fstaff escaped unharmed.
