OL,6,FShe said the schoolgirls were
OL,7,F'hysterical' following the fire, and
OL,8,Fthe class ran to shelter under a
OL,9,Ftunnel to escape the 'burning grass'
OL,10,Fon the side of the motorway caused by
OL,11,Fthe fire.
OL,13,F"We took them to McDonald's in Bolton
OL,14,Fto keep them safe and they were given
OL,15,Ffree colouring things to keep them
OL,16,Fcalm, that was really good.
OL,18,F"The police helped us get them back to
OL,19,Fschool where they were given
OL,20,Fcounselling to make sure they were
OL,21,Fokay."
