OL,7,FPolice (GMP) said: "It's the sort of
OL,8,Fcall we really dread! A coach carrying
OL,9,FTeachers and 30+ Kids on fire at busy
OL,10,FM60 slip.
OL,12,F"A fantastic response from @gmptraffic
OL,13,F@manchesterfire @NationalHways
OL,14,F@NWAmbulance safely evacuated driver
OL,15,Fand all passengers. Not all heroes
OL,16,Fwear capes!"
